OL,3,CHow will Ofgem's #28bn investment
OL,4,Cimpact your energy bills?
OL,6,FBritain's energy watchdog has given
OL,7,Fthe green light to a #28 billion
OL,8,Fupgrade of the UK's energy
OL,9,Finfrastructure, warning that it will
OL,10,Flikely push up household bills.
OL,12,FOfgem said the investment package will
OL,13,F"strengthen the stability, security
OL,14,Fand resilience of our energy networks"
OL,15,Fwhile supporting the transition to new
OL,16,Fand cleaner forms of energy.
