OL,3,CHow will Ofgem's #28bn investment
OL,4,Cimpact your energy bills?
OL,6,FThe National Grid, which runs much of
OL,7,FBritain's electricity grid, said it
OL,8,Fwelcomed Ofgem's "recognition of the
OL,9,Fneed for significant investment into
OL,10,Fthe electricity transmission sector".
OL,12,FThe announcement comes after Ofgem
OL,13,Fannounced the energy price cap would
OL,14,Frise unexpectedly in January, despite
OL,15,Fforecasts that it would go down.
OL,17,FSo what impact will this investment
OL,18,Fpackage have on ordinary households,
OL,19,Fand when can they expect their energy
OL,20,Fbills to come down? ITV News explains.
