OL,3,CHow will Ofgem's #28bn investment
OL,4,Cimpact your energy bills?
OL,6,FWhat is #28 billion being invested in?
OL,8,FMost of the funding (#17.8 billion)
OL,9,Fannounced on Thursday will go towards
OL,10,F"maintaining Britain's gas networks,
OL,11,Fkeeping them among the safest, most
OL,12,Fsecure and resilient in the world,"
OL,13,FOfgem said.
OL,15,FThe remaining initial investment
OL,16,F(#10.3 billion) will help "strengthen
OL,17,Four electricity transmission network,
OL,18,Fimprove reliability and expand
OL,19,Fcapacity to support the
OL,20,Felectrification of the economy and
OL,21,Fdrive growth", the regulator said.
