OL,3,CHow will Ofgem's #28bn investment
OL,4,Cimpact your energy bills?
OL,6,FTheapprovedinvestment willfund 80
OL,7,Fprojects over the nextfive years,
OL,8,Fincluding new power lines,
OL,9,Fsubstations, and technologies to
OL,10,Fhandle the flow of electricity from
OL,11,Fnew renewable sources.
OL,13,FWhat impact will this have on
OL,14,Fhousehold bills?
OL,16,FOfgem said its decision to increase
OL,17,Fthe allowed investment spend will push
OL,18,Fup household bills by more than first
OL,19,Fexpected, before savings.
