OL,3,CHow will Ofgem's #28bn investment
OL,4,Cimpact your energy bills?
OL,6,FHouseholds will see the network
OL,7,Fcharges on bills, which make up around
OL,8,Fa fifth of average annual energy
OL,9,Fcosts, surge by #108 by 2031 to cover
OL,10,Fthe cost of the extra investment.
OL,12,FThis is up from the #104 rise
OL,13,Festimated in its draft verdict in
OL,14,FJuly. Ofgem said this will include #48
OL,15,Ffor gas networks and #60 for the
OL,16,Felectricity grid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
