OL,3,CHow will Ofgem's #28bn investment
OL,4,Cimpact your energy bills?
OL,6,FHowever, the regulator insisted that
OL,7,Fbills would be even higher without the
OL,8,Fapproved investment, with the funding
OL,9,Falso expected to save the UK money on
OL,10,Fimported gas by boosting the nation's
OL,11,Fpower generation.
OL,13,FIt added that with savings of around
OL,14,F#80 taken into account, the net
OL,15,Fincrease to bills is expected to be
OL,16,Faround #30, or #3 a month.
OL,18,FCosts are expected to fall in future
OL,19,Fyears as more renewable electricity
OL,20,Fgeneration will lower wholesale power
OL,21,Fcosts.
