OL,3,CHow will Ofgem's #28bn investment
OL,4,Cimpact your energy bills?
OL,6,FJonathan Brearley, chief executive of
OL,7,FOfgem, said: "The investment will
OL,8,Fsupport the transition to new forms of
OL,9,Fenergy and support new industrial
OL,10,Fcustomers to help drive economic
OL,11,Fgrowth and insulate us from volatile
OL,12,Fgas prices.
OL,14,F"But this is not an investment at any
OL,15,Fprice. Every pound must deliver value
OL,16,Ffor consumers.
