OL,3,CHow will Ofgem's #28bn investment
OL,4,Cimpact your energy bills?
OL,6,FWholesale energy prices increased
OL,7,Frapidly from the second half of 2021
OL,8,Fand much of 2022.
OL,10,FThis is partly due to pressures in
OL,11,Finternational supply chains as the
OL,12,Fglobal economy recovered from the
OL,13,FCovid-19 pandemic, and also due to
OL,14,FRussia's invasion of Ukraine's impact
OL,15,Fon energy markets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
