OL,3,CHow will Ofgem's #28bn investment
OL,4,Cimpact your energy bills?
OL,6,FMany consumers were protected, at
OL,7,Fleast initially, by the energy price
OL,8,Fcap, a system regulated by Ofgem that
OL,9,Frestricts the amount that energy
OL,10,Fsuppliers can charge for each unit of
OL,11,Fgas and electricity.
OL,13,FBut the cap was increased by 54% in
OL,14,FApril 2022, and substantially again in
OL,15,FOctober 2022. This period marked the
OL,16,F"largest ever" annual increases on
OL,17,Fseries going back to 1970, a Commons
OL,18,Fresearch briefing said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
